text:
Google Scholar Error 403 解决办法
按上述方法搭建v2ray，虽然可以科学上网，但是唯独无法访问Google Scholar. 会遇到错误

Your client does not have permission to get URL/from this server

这是因为Scholar 风控比较严格, 一般 VPS 的 IP 都会被 Scholar 屏蔽。解决方法是在VPS上安装 Cloudflare warp, 二次代理到 Cloudflare 的网络来访问 Scholar.
在 cf warp 官网 下载 cf warp 的 Linux 安装包 (.deb文件). 用scp 传送到VPS上进行安装，然后开启socks代理：
warp-cli register
warp-cli set-mode proxy
warp-cli set-proxy-port 1249
warp-cli connect
最后这个端口号可以自行选择。然后打开v2ray配置文件
vim /etc/v2ray/config.json
修改相应模块如下：（注意socks的端口是上面设置的端口）
 "outbounds": [
    {
      "protocol": "freedom",
      "settings": {}
    },
    {
      "protocol": "blackhole",
      "settings": {},
      "tag": "block"
    },
    {
      "protocol": "socks",
      "settings": {
        "version": "5",
        "servers": [
          {
            "address": "127.0.0.1",
            "port": 1249
          }
        ]
      },
       "tag": "scholar"
    }
  ],

"routing": {
    "domainStrategy": "AsIs",
    "rules": [
      {
        "type": "field",
        "ip": [
          "0.0.0.0/8",
          "10.0.0.0/8",
          "100.64.0.0/10",
          "169.254.0.0/16",
          "172.16.0.0/12",
          "192.0.0.0/24",
          "192.0.2.0/24",
          "192.168.0.0/16",
          "198.18.0.0/15",
          "198.51.100.0/24",
          "203.0.113.0/24",
          "::1/128",
          "fc00::/7",
          "fe80::/10"
        ],
        "outboundTag": "block"
      },
      {
        "type": "field",
        "domains": [
          "scholar.google",
          "scholar.googleusercontent",
          "www.cloudflare.com"
        ],
        "outboundTag": "scholar"
      }
    ]
  }
重启 v2ray 后即可正常访问 Google Scholar.
